OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA dry start, before
OL,6,Fincreasing cloud and outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, locally heavy, spreads east
OL,8,Facross all parts during the day.
OL,9,FWindy, locally gusty on hills. Feeling
OL,10,Fhumid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,13,Fcloud and brighter spells, with some
OL,14,Fscattered light showers on Friday,
OL,15,Fthese easing later. Breezy. Dry with
OL,16,Fsunny spells on Saturday and Sunday.
OL,17,FFeeling warmer, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
